      <b>
       Jeremia treurend over de verwoesting van Jeruzalem
      </b>
      (easel painting (painting by form); Rembrandt Harmensz. van Rijn (Leiden 1606-07-15 - Amsterdam ...; 1630; Rijksmuseum (Amsterdam, North Holland, Netherlands); SK-A-3276; RM001.collect.5242)
     </td>
